                            <br />
                            客服信箱: <a href="mailto:marketplace@newegg.com.tw" target="_self" >marketplace@newegg.com.tw</a>
                            <br />
                            服務時間: 週一至週五 <span style="color:blue;font-weight:900;" class="FontArial">8:30a.m.~12:00 p.m. 1:00p.m.~5:30 p.m</span>
